{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act11d0_level_act11d0_02_beg","storyGroup":"act11d0","storySort":4,"storyDependence":"act11d0_level_act11d0_01_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"TW-2","storyName":"叛乱前哨","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"在寻访沃伦姆德街道的途中，亚叶询问着当地少女塔佳娜有关安托的事情，但众人却不小心撞入了感染者集会的现场引起了感染者的攻击。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act11d0/level_act11d0_02_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act11d0_02","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":2,"next":4,"characters":["铃兰","亚叶","镇民","塔佳娜"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"九尾狐活动 2上","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"Dialog","id":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_ltstreet1","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_ltalley","screenadapt":"coverall","id":8},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":9},{"type":"Text","text":"3:59 P.M.    天气/多云","id":10},{"type":"Text","text":"移动城镇沃伦姆德，感染者居住区，十二音街道","id":11},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":12},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"$darkness01_loop","volume":"0.4","id":13,"musicid":0},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":14},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"亚叶姐姐......你在生气吗？","id":15,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":16},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"他们的态度意味着什么，我太清楚了......","id":17,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"但是，但是安托不会有事的，她比我们任何人都熟悉莱塔尼亚！","id":18,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":19},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"嗯！安托姐姐一定没事的。","id":20,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"但愿......","id":21,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#2"},{"type":"Dialog","id":22},{"type":"Character","id":23},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.3","id":24},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_065","id":25},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"......","id":26,"figure":"avg_npc_065"},{"type":"Character","id":27},{"type":"Dialog","id":28},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":29},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.3","id":30},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_068","id":31},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"......","id":32,"figure":"avg_npc_068"},{"type":"Character","id":33},{"type":"Dialog","id":34},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":35},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","id":36},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"总觉得这附近有点安静得可怕......？","id":37,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"2","id":38},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"嗯，跟紧点。","id":39,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"看上去不光有普通的居民，还有很多感染者，不过这不是重点。","id":40,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"刚才阻止那些暴徒的时候我就在想了，这个街道的规模，怎么看都只是普通的街区吧？","id":41,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"只是把感染者们集中起来生活，并没有什么明面上的差别对待。","id":42,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"1","id":43},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"嗯......","id":44,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":45},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"但实际上，感染者依旧被约束了人身自由，而且除了那些能够“物尽其用”的感染者，大部分人这辈子和坐牢没什么区别......","id":46,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"只不过牢狱变成了一条街道，多了几十倍的狱友罢了。","id":47,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"看这儿，这家面包店多久没有开过门了？","id":48,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"1","id":49},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"啊......我好像看到源石虫爬过去了......好不卫生啊。","id":50,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"2","id":51},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"店门口的灰尘和落叶都没人打扫，这个社区没有在正常运作。","id":52,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"虽说是在特殊时期，但街上见不到一个买卖面包的人？公共交通也停摆了，这也太不自然了......","id":53,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"1","id":54},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"因为，因为之前的事情？店主被吓走了之类的？","id":55,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"2","id":56},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"但至少他们还有活着的权利，他们——","id":57,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#3"},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":58},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","id":59},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"亚叶姐姐......！声音小点！嘘！","id":60,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#3"},{"type":"Dialog","id":61},{"type":"Character","id":62},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"......","id":63},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":64},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......我没有在指责他们，我只是说......关于“武装感染者”的话题。","id":65,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":66},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"他们会是......","id":67,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"2","id":68},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"那个宪兵提到了“萨卡兹”，这是首先要确定的事情。","id":69,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"如果真的和我们所知道的“感染者武装组织”有关，我们必须警觉起来。这里的情况也许比那个宪兵说的还要复杂。","id":70,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"1","id":71},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"是这样吗？","id":72,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"2","id":73},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"如果感染者的情况够好，那只是因为处境还不够绝望。","id":74,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"他们肯定还有事情瞒着我们。","id":75,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"1","id":76},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"亚叶姐姐？","id":77,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"不用那么紧张喔，安托姐姐可是很聪明的。","id":78,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":79},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"我......","id":80,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":81},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"从刚才开始，亚叶姐姐就一直是很可怕的状态嘛。没关系的。","id":82,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"只要我们好好努力，就能出色地解决这件事，就像各位干员前辈那样！","id":83,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"所以稍微放轻松一点吧？","id":84,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#2","focus":"2","id":85},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......哈，我又被小丽萨安慰了？这是怎么了？","id":86,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#2","focus":"1","id":87},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"嘿嘿，烦恼不分大小啦。","id":88,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":89},{"type":"Character","id":90},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.6","id":91},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":92},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":93},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_069#4","id":94},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"二位，请稍等——！","id":95,"figure":"avg_npc_069#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_345_folnic_1#3","id":96},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"是你？","id":97,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"我记得我说过我们不需要帮助，只需要权限就......","id":98,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_069#4","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"1","id":99},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"抱歉，虽然亚叶小姐那么说了，但是毕竟情况特殊，二位人生地不熟的，如果出了什么意外，我们无法承担。","id":100,"figure":"avg_npc_069#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"1","id":101},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"......亚叶姐姐。","id":102,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":103},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"好吧......如果有本地人在身边，也许这里的居民也不会这么害怕我们了吧。","id":104,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_069","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":105},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"没错！咳咳！十二音街道原本是沃伦姆德最大的感染者聚集区......","id":106,"figure":"avg_npc_069"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_069","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":107},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"不过现在因为某些原因，这里也是抗议者最多的地方。","id":108,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":109},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"所以亚叶小姐，现在打算怎么做？","id":110,"figure":"avg_npc_069#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"其实我并不是很建议深入这里......不过如果您想了解沃伦姆德的现状，这的确是个好选择。","id":111,"figure":"avg_npc_069#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":112},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......先四处逛逛吧，没必要操之过急。","id":113,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"如果你愿意说点关于安托医生的事情，我会很高兴的。","id":114,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":115},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"亚叶小姐......真的很关心安托医生呢。","id":116,"figure":"avg_npc_069#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":117},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"她是我的同学，是我为数不多的好友，更是罗德岛不可或缺的成员。","id":118,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":119},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"......是吗。","id":120,"figure":"avg_npc_069#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"啊，请往这边走，这里是通往秋千广场的路。","id":121,"figure":"avg_npc_069#2"},{"type":"Dialog","id":122},{"type":"Character","id":123},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":124},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":125},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_ltalley","screenadapt":"coverall","id":126},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":127},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":128},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"安托在这里做了什么？","id":129,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":130},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"啊......医治这里的感染者，帮助那些被感染的人做心理辅导。","id":131,"figure":"avg_npc_069#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"因为天灾信使的失误，沃伦姆德镇没能在大裂谷出现前及时避开，遭到了不小的损失。","id":132,"figure":"avg_npc_069#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"安托医生有机会离开这里，但是她选择了留下。沃伦姆德停泊在现在的位置之后，她建立起了临时医疗据点，为了更好地安置感染者们。","id":133,"figure":"avg_npc_069#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"安托医生她......被当做这里感染者们的英雄。","id":134,"figure":"avg_npc_069#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#2","focus":"2","id":135},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......这是她应该做的。","id":136,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"嗯，没错，比起死板的学习，她果然更适合实践。","id":137,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#2","focus":"1","id":138},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"......","id":139,"figure":"avg_npc_069#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_069#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"2","id":140},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......呵呵，是啊，真好，我都能想象到她一脸得意的样子。","id":141,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_069","name2":"char_345_folnic_1","focus":"1","id":142},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"亚叶小姐，这是您造访沃伦姆德后第一次笑容呢。","id":143,"figure":"avg_npc_069"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_069","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":144},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......有吗？","id":145,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":146},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"今天的亚叶姐姐大部分时间都很吓人。","id":147,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":148},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"欸......","id":149,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#4"},{"type":"Character","id":150},{"type":"Dialog","id":151},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_068","name2":"avg_npc_065","id":152},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":153},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1","id":154},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"前面......前面有好多人，这附近的人都聚集在这里了吗？","id":155,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_069","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":156},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......不用管？","id":157,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_069","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":158},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"只是聚在一起的话，也不能成为逮捕他们的理由吧？","id":159,"figure":"avg_npc_069"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_069#4","id":160},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"他们看过来了......","id":161,"figure":"avg_npc_069#4"},{"type":"Dialog","id":162},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":163},{"type":"Character","id":164},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_065","id":165},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"......","id":166,"figure":"avg_npc_065"},{"type":"Character","id":167},{"type":"Dialog","id":168},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":169},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_068","id":170},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"......","id":171,"figure":"avg_npc_068"},{"type":"Character","id":172},{"type":"Dialog","id":173},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":174},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":175},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"怎么突然就安静下来了？","id":176,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"2","id":177},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......不，情况不太对......他们在听谁说话？","id":178,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_069#4","id":179},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"欸？","id":180,"figure":"avg_npc_069#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_345_folnic_1#3","id":181},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"站在他们身后的，站在人群最后的那个——","id":182,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"是个，萨卡兹吗......？","id":183,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_069#4","id":184},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"萨卡兹......？","id":185,"figur